      <title>里夫斯誓言“修正方向”以恢复英国的财富</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/reeves-vows-course-correction-to-restore-uk-economic-fortunes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反对党工党候任财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯承诺对英国经济进行根本性的“路线修正”，称英国需要投资于增长并解决潜在的结构性问题，以打破停滞的束缚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/reeves-vows-course-correction-to-restore-uk-economic-fortunes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
